Consistency:
\f1\b0  Only transactions that abide by constraints and rules are written into the database, otherwise the database keeps the previous state. The data should be correct across all rows and tables. Check out additional information about consistency on {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Consistency_%28database_systems%29"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 Wikipedia}}.\cb1 \
