Durability:
\f1\b0  Completed transactions are saved to database even in cases of system failure. A commonly cited example includes tracking flight seat bookings. So once the flight booking records a confirmed seat booking, the seat remains booked even if a system failure occurs. Source: {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ACID"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 Wikipedia}}.}